HEADWORD: expropriated
<hw>expropriated</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>taken out of the possession
of another and transferred to one's own use often without permission;
<as>as, the <ex>expropriated</ex> land was developed into a public
playground</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

